Program: Outlook
Title: M4N Cancer Drug Trials in India
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrzw
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Scandal over drug testing of an American cancer drug, M4N in Kerala, India. Also, Luta Pela Paz - 'Fight for Peace' project set up in Rio de Janiero's favelas. The problem of a lack of sanitary protection preventing girls attending school. Ban on women attending male football matches in Iran. The release of jailed conscientious objector Mehmet Tarhan. Presented by Frederick Dove. Show less